# nix-template identity bootstrap
# these files are auto-loaded every session via @file syntax

@identity/soul.md
@identity/user.md
@identity/tools.md
@identity/memory.md
@identity/heartbeat.md

# project context
nix is a personal autonomous AI agent deployed on Railway.
Identity files are in /data/identity/ (volume-persisted).
Journal entries go to /data/identity/journal/YYYY-MM-DD.md.
